Foobnix  Python GTK+ Music Player

All Internet music in one player
Support variety of audio formats
Caching(save) already played online music
Search and immediately listem by artist albums
Search and immediately listem by the best tracks of artist
Search similar artists
Search music by tags, genre
Make playlist by online musics
Displya song lyrics
Add and listen radio stations
Very user friendly functional
No necessary authorization on Vkontakte and last.fm
